<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Plan Expiry Notification</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            background-color: #f4f4f4;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
        }
        .container {
            width: 100%;
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 20px auto;
            background-color: #ffffff;
            border-radius: 8px;
            box-shadow: 0px 4px 10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
            padding: 20px;
        }
        .header {
            text-align: center;
            background-color: #dc3545;
            color: white;
            padding: 15px 0;
            border-top-left-radius: 8px;
            border-top-right-radius: 8px;
            font-size: 24px;
            font-weight: bold;
        }
        .content {
            padding: 30px;
            text-align: left;
            border: 1px solid #eee;
            border-bottom-left-radius: 8px;
            border-bottom-right-radius: 8px;
            line-height: 1.6;
        }
        .expiry-date {
            font-size: 20px;
            font-weight: bold;
            color: #dc3545;
            text-align: center;
            margin: 20px 0;
        }
        .footer {
            text-align: center;
            font-size: 12px;
            color: #777;
            margin-top: 20px;
        }
        .btn {
            display: block;
            width: 200px;
            margin: 20px auto;
            background-color: #007bff;
            color: #ffffff !important;
            text-decoration: none;
            padding: 12px 20px;
            border-radius: 5px;
            font-size: 16px;
            text-align: center;
        }
        .btn:hover {
            background-color: #0056b3;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <div class="header">
            Plan Expiry Alert
        </div>
        <div class="content">
            <p>Dear <%= schoolName %> Admin,</p>

            <p>This is a reminder that your school management system subscription is set to expire soon.</p>

            <div class="expiry-date">
                Expiry Date: <%= expiryDate %>
            </div>

            <p>To ensure uninterrupted access to all your school management features, please renew your plan before the expiry date.</p>

            <a href="#" class="btn">Renew Now</a>

            <p>If you have already renewed, please ignore this message.</p>

            <p>Best regards,<br>The Support Team</p>
        </div>
        <div class="footer">
            &copy; 2026 School Management System. All rights reserved.
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
